        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> I was thinking Verant should turn this into a Rez Stone ie: right click but maybe another type of stone and spell would be better call it a "Soul Stone" etc. It follows the same got to kill someone and the lose exp principal but it wields you a tradeable Rez Stone (96% Rez) you simply Target the corpse and right click the stone and the person is rezzed all classes could use it ie: a actual market for the stone. I think people would pay a hefty share to carry a 96% exp rez in their pocket. </P><P>Bezel Ubub</P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
